{"tid":2358489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽黨話，跟黨走","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T07:27:52.000Z","uid":386601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a976bd2701bb9939bc848a0388a74a9aab11c395","tid":2358489,"uid":386601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:26:25.000Z","msg":"大家準備好了沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210108/FSU5VHDR5FBUHFG7WHDFRMW74U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210108%2FFSU5VHDR5FBUHFG7WHDFRMW74U%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIbyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=de7857bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210108%2FFSU5VHDR5FBUHFG7WHDFRMW74U%2F&h=deba1243\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210108/FSU5VHDR5FBUHFG7WHDFRMW74U/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0T7tOJ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0T7tOJ0.png&h=c54cdda6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gu1N4hm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGu1N4hm.png&h=6d73d276&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJydfo2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJydfo2.png&h=7c798325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大帽山是本港最高的山峯，經常吸引市民到來遊玩，閒時遠足，秋天賞芒草，冬天賞霜。不過，最近有市民發現，大帽山頂的雷達站，建築物外牆竟然驚現「听党话 跟党走」、「法纪严 风气正」簡體字標語，甚至山坡上亦髹上疑似中國國旗的圖案，儼如內地大部份的國家建築物外貌，令人相當震撼。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者今早走到大帽山頂的雷達站，果然見到所述情況。建築物頂樓外牆，掛上紅色簡體字宣傳標語「听党话 跟党走」；低層外牆同樣是紅色簡體字「法纪严 风气正」，路面一道石壆有黃色字「忠诚坚毅」；右邊山坡則畫上五星地圖。有行山人士表示，建築物外牆的簡體字，是於近日才掛出。<br />\n<br />\n雷達站有鐵閘，鐵閘外有警告牌標示為「禁區」：「此區禁止任何未得許可者進入」、「此區內的任何建設禁止攝影繪圖及製模等」。其間記者見到一名穿迷彩制服的人員，由圓頂建築物步行去另一幢建築物，落山時亦見到解放軍專用車牌「ZG」字頭的車輛，獲管理員放行直駛上山。"},{"pid":"f6f2d78ff35638014fa34ead0c803de0ec12dc1d","tid":2358489,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dad0a7b44f48d67e832334e9443692c1a28a6f","tid":2358489,"uid":388788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"Old News"}]}